(1, 5344, 'national-tot-feedback-meeting', 1, 1, 'National ToT Feedback Meeting', '09:00:00', '09:00:00', 0, '2016-06-06', '2016-06-06', 'National ToT Feedback meeting will run from 6 - 10 June 2016. The main purpose of this meeting is to: -\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Review the National EMR Strategic Plan - Draft one</li>\r\n 	<li>Final testing of the UganaEMR System before the mass scaleup</li>\r\n 	<li>Final review of the UgandaEMR user manual and training materials</li>\r\n 	<li>The venue and particpants for this meeting will be communicated soon!</li>\r\n</ol>', 0, NULL, '00:00:00', NULL, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 'a:1:{s:14:"slide_template";s:7:"default";}', '2016-11-10 06:13:42', '2016-11-10 06:14:35', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0),
(2, 5347, 'national-openmrs-tot', 1, 1, 'National OpenMRS ToT', '09:00:00', '09:00:00', 0, '2016-05-02', '2016-05-02', 'The Ministry of Health - Division of Health Information in collaboration with Makerere University School of Public Health METS program and WHO have planned for a five (5) day OpenMRS Training of Trainers workshop on 2nd - 6th May 2016. The training will take place at Lake View Hotel, Mbarara.\r\n\r\nThe main objective of the workshop is to provide participants with practical hands-on training on the updated OpenMRS system. Specifically, the training seeks to:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Build Capacity to Upgrade existing OpenMRS installations (1.6.3 to 1.11.6)</li>\r\n 	<li>Give technical guidance on troubleshooting the new features and functionalities of upgraded OpenMRS.</li>\r\n 	<li>Provide training on report generation and data use</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nSee you there.\r\n\r\n<strong>Agenda:</strong>\r\n<a href="http://127.0.0.1/emr/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/National-OpenMRS-ToT-Agenda-Final-2016.pdf">national-openmrs-tot-agenda-final-2016</a>', 0, NULL, '00:00:00', NULL, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 'a:0:{}', '2016-11-10 06:22:35', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0),
